description: Record to support submission of GeneRIFs for a gene not in Gene (Agrobacterium genomic group 7; Agrobacterium genomic species 7; Agrobacterium genomic species G7; Agrobacterium genomosp. 7; Agrobacterium tumefaciens genomovar G7.  Use when strain, subtype, isolate, etc. is unspecified, or when different from all specified ones in Gene.).
